\b\fs30 2) Sample Project 1: Facebook Marketplace Listing Transfer\b0\fs24\par
\par
\b\fs27 Task Overview\b0\fs24\par
The task involves copying a product listing from Facebook Marketplace and transferring it into a structured website product page format while preserving all key details such as title, price, condition, and description.\par
\par
\b\fs27 Original Marketplace Listing\b0\fs24\par
\tab\bullet\tab **Product Title:** Samsung Galaxy S21 128GB (Unlocked) – Phantom Gray\par
\tab\bullet\tab **Price:** $320\par
\tab\bullet\tab **Location:** Austin, TX\par
\tab\bullet\tab **Condition:** Used – Like New\par
\tab\bullet\tab **Description:**\par
  Selling my Samsung Galaxy S21, 128GB, unlocked for all carriers. Phone is in excellent condition with no cracks or major scratches. Battery health is strong and all functions work perfectly. Includes original charging cable and a protective case. Local pickup preferred.\par
\par
\b\fs27 Website Listing Entry\b0\fs24\par
\tab\bullet\tab **Product Name:** Samsung Galaxy S21 128GB Unlocked Smartphone (Phantom Gray)\par
\tab\bullet\tab **Category:** Electronics > Mobile Phones\par
\tab\bullet\tab **Price:** USD 320.00\par
\tab\bullet\tab **Condition:** Like New (Pre-Owned)\par
\tab\bullet\tab **Full Product Description:**\par
  Samsung Galaxy S21 with 128GB storage in Phantom Gray, fully unlocked and compatible with major carriers. Device is pre-owned and maintained in like-new condition, with no screen cracks and minimal signs of use. Battery performance remains strong, and all core features (camera, speakers, charging port, and buttons) are fully functional. Includes charging cable and protective case. Available for local pickup in Austin, Texas.\par
\tab\bullet\tab **Tags:** samsung, galaxy s21, unlocked phone, smartphone, 128gb, phantom gray, pre-owned\par
