\par
\b\fs27 Accuracy Notes\b0\fs24\par
To ensure accuracy, each field from the original Marketplace listing was mapped to a matching website field and reviewed line-by-line. Price format was standardized (USD with decimals), condition wording was normalized for CMS consistency, and descriptive details (carrier status, accessories, pickup location) were retained to prevent information loss.\par
