\b\fs30 5) Sample Project 4: Listing Transfer Workflow\b0\fs24\par
\par
\b\fs27 Workflow for Transferring Listings Between Platforms\b0\fs24\par
1. Open the source marketplace listing.\par
2. Copy product title, price, condition, and description.\par
3. Download or collect listing images.\par
4. Open the destination website CMS product form.\par
5. Paste product details into the correct fields.\par
6. Assign product category and relevant tags.\par
7. Upload and arrange images in display order.\par
8. Add SKU, inventory details, and listing status.\par
9. Publish or save as draft based on client preference.\par
10. Perform a final quality check for completeness and formatting.\par
\par
This workflow ensures repeatable quality, faster turnaround, and consistent listing standards across platforms.\par
